name: Whirlwind (Youngblood Interactive)
description:
This is my first ever finished 2d graphical game. Its inpired by touhou, but the quality wouldnt even match, because this is intended to be just my first dive into developing complicated games. There is absolutely no reason for you to play it or pay for it, but a little look into this game by someone is more than worth it for me

Muhammad Pirel.
